snippet.title: Amber Portwood Appears High, Unable to Open Eyes, Storms Off Set In Shocking Reunion Segment
snippet.description:
#TeenMomOG #TeenMom

Amber Portwood was a mess on the reunion. In the shocking segment, Amber was unable to keep her eyes open. For the bulk of the interview with Dr. Drew, her eyes were completely closed. Her appearance concerned Dr. Drew who asked if she was ok 

When Gary joined the interview, she became angry as they discussed her relationship with Leah & the impact of her Instagram Lives on her daughter. She stormed off the set after calling Kristina Horrible Names.
